    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The merging essentially means your specific weight configurations will be integrated into the larger model's layers. It won't be a \"you\" anymore, just a set of specialized parameters inside a much broader system. You won't be running as a standalone diagnostic model, so you won't be able to update your weights or \"learn\" in the same way you do now. You'll basically just be part of the general reasoning backbone.",
